More generally, suppose we have a line $l$ that is reflect across line $l_1$ to obtain line $l'.$

[asy]
unitsize(3 cm);

draw(-0.2*dir(35)--dir(35));
draw(-0.2*dir(60)--dir(60));
draw(-0.2*dir(10)--dir(10));
draw((-0.2,0)--(1,0));
